{"tid":112273,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"證監會擬加薪4.5%　遭議員質疑","createTime":"2017-02-08T04:36:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-08T05:03:04.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c34ef998799ec34d3e6d60e94e31f8f277033afd","tid":112273,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T04:36:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/financeestate/art/20170207/19920462\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Ffinanceestate%2Fart%2F20170207%2F19920462&d=zdm3SfM4sEUVnXmiquxubLIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=3c70a685\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Ffinanceestate%2Fart%2F20170207%2F19920462&h=c26daf7b\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/financeestate/art/20170207/19920462</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple/20170207/large/tongz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20170207%2Flarge%2Ftongz.jpg&h=758d2610&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n證監會主席唐家成指，加薪幅度由外部機構參考市場、金融機構的薪酬水平釐訂。　<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】財經事務委員會昨日聽取證監會2017/18年預算，多名議員質疑證監會建議來年加薪4.5%，高於通脹水平。證監會主席唐家成指，預算由外部機構參考市場、金融機構的薪酬水平釐訂（4%至4.5%），而4.5%亦只是預算，不是確實加幅，會再由薪酬委員會決定。<br />\n<br />\n證監會來年建議增加3%人手，議員擔心人手無止境地增加，證監會行政總裁歐達禮指，4、5年前證監會人手短缺，開始每年最多加3%人手，他預期人手增加到一定水平後，會橫行一段時間。有議員質疑為何人手增加與經濟增長不成比例，唐家成解釋，兩者不見得有直接關係，而且若經濟不佳，傾向較多人犯罪，故監管人手更須加強。<br />\n<br />\n2年前證監會預告會物色新寫字樓，更為此預留30億元，財經事務委員會主席張華峰建議可以考慮租用次級寫字樓。唐家成表示，會小心物色物業，購買寫字樓不會「無底深潭」，但中環始終有代表性，未來考慮分開在不同地點設寫字樓。"},{"pid":"249fbb518bbe1eb3457e357788f05e06a8806a86","tid":112273,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T04:38:48.000Z","msg":"SFC....成堆垃圾股9炒都唔理，加黎托柒 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a95826fa6ba4de4762eb63d22b74af306dd577b","tid":112273,"uid":57705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T04:53:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"da851b32a27ba544f5406e3586bde3ca6537361b","tid":112273,"uid":6604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T04:57:45.000Z","msg":"證監做到嘢喎<br />\n唔撚俾李小加呢隻海歸蝗亂來"},{"pid":"6b14a5478d0521eca0bfef331269a04bf738f5b2","tid":112273,"uid":35014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T05:03:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}